Body:
Is it possible to install other versions of windows aside windows IoT Core when using Intel Joule 570? I need full windows 7/8/10 functionality if possible.
Is it out of scope for Joule?
Thanks

Intel Joule currently supports

  • Windows 10 IoT Core
  • Ubuntu 16.04 LTS
  • Ubuntu Core
  • Ref-OS-IoT

But not full versions of window 7
Thanks. Is enterprise similar in any way to win 10 ?? GUI, app installations (exe win32) etc etc?
Just Core, I have edited my answer to reflect that. Enterprise can be installed, but many drivers are missing, and some things just don't work.
Do you mean Windows IoT enterprise as well? or just core edition
